The Glenn Beck Program - 08/08/13


Thursday, August 08, 2013 12:31 PM





Glenn and the guys discuss Lindsey Graham's fact finding mission to Egypt,
 and how everything that's happening over there is "news to him".

 Also discusses how congress and their staffers are getting a waiver on Obamacare 
 and how we must call our senators to defund it.

 Also discusses Tara Reid and the Animal Kingdom,

 the IRS possibly using DEA data illegally 

 and a how Colorado apartment complex may be taking away constitutional rights from their tenants.
